  "original_title": "\u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba \u0d86\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dca\u0dc2\u0d9a \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0db8\u0d9a\u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd9\u0d9a\u0dd4 \u0db4\u0dc4\u0dbb\u0daf\u0dd3 \u0daf\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca\u0dbb\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0db4\u0dd2\u0da7\u0dad\u0da7 \u0dad\u0dbd\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd4\u0d9a\u0dbb \u0d9d\u0dcf\u0dad\u0db1\u0dba \u0d9a\u0dbb\u0dba\u0dd2",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A railway guard is beaten and pushed out of the train and killed",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Police say that a railway security guard who was on duty in the inter-city express train running from Colombo Fort to Jaffna was attacked and pushed out of the train at Wayangoda, Wandurawa.",
        "The police say that during a search operation based on information received by the Police 119 emergency number, the dead body of a railway security guard was found at a distance of 100 meters from the Vandurava Police Station to Mirigama Dema.",
        "A 52-year-old resident of Ulayagoda Road, Oruthota has lost his life. A complaint has been made to the railway security department that two passengers were traveling under the influence of alcohol in a train compartment.",
        "The security officers have made arrangements to check in this regard, and when the two were being taken out of the carriage by the railway security guards, the guard was thrown out of the train after one person kicked a guard.",
        "The two intoxicated persons were caught by the police and handed over to the train security department and then handed over to the Mirigama police station.",
        "The police say that the suspects are aged 31 and 23 and are residents of Nochchiyagama and Anuradhapura."
      ],
